## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability and reliability of online sources, which may contain biased or unverified information. Additionally, the perspectives gathered are not exhaustive and may not represent the full spectrum of reasons for vaccine hesitancy. Further research, including empirical studies and surveys, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of this issue.